OL,3,CEurosport Olympics commentator
OL,4,Capologises after sexist remark about
OL,5,Cswimmers
OL,7,FA seasoned sports commentator has
OL,8,Fapologised after he made sexist
OL,9,Fremarks about one of Australia's
OL,10,Ffemale swimmers at the Paris 2024
OL,11,FOlympics.
OL,13,FIn a clip which went viral on social
OL,14,Fmedia, Bob Ballard said: "Well, the
OL,15,Fwomen just finishing up. You know what
OL,16,Fwomen are like...hanging around, doing
OL,17,Ftheir makeup."
