OL,4,Capologises after sexist remark about
OL,5,Cswimmers
OL,7,FThe commentator posted on social media
OL,8,Fto apologise for the remarks and said:
OL,9,F"The comments I made during the
OL,10,FAustralian freestyle relay victory
OL,11,Fceremony on Saturday have caused some
OL,12,Foffence. It was never my intention to
OL,13,Fupset or belittle anyone and, if I
OL,14,Fdid, I apologise. I am a massive
OL,15,Fadvocate of women's sport.
OL,17,F"I shall miss the Eurosport team,
OL,18,Fdearly and wish them all the best for
OL,19,Fthe rest of the Olympics."
