OL,7,FHis co-commentator Lizzie Simmonds
OL,8,Fcalled the remark "outrageous".
OL,10,FA statement from the broadcaster said:
OL,11,F"During a segment of Eurosport's
OL,12,Fcoverage last night, commentator Bob
OL,13,FBallard made an inappropriate comment.
OL,14,FTo that end, he has been removed from
OL,15,Four commentary roster with immediate
OL,16,Feffect."
